成的提要）&lt;/span&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 19 Mar 2026 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.rand.org/pubs/working_papers/WRA4869-1.html</guid></item><item><title>哪些因素推动采用高质量的数学课程和专业学习？来自美国的横切调查结果...</title><link>https://www.rand.org/pubs/research_reports/RRA4632-1.html</link><description>&lt;img height="90" src="https://www.rand.org/content/rand/pubs/research_reports/RRA4632-1/_jcr_content/par/teaser_copy.crop.160x90.cm.jpeg/1774035278145.jpeg" width="160" /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;p class="desc"&gt;采用高质量的教学材料可以极大地帮助学生的学习。为了更好地理解这一过程，本报告的作者探讨了地区和学校如何采用数学课程和相关专业学习。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt; &lt;span style="font-size: 12px; color: gray;"&gt;（使用&lt;a href="https://fetchrss.com/feedLink?w=67d7ba1d141b09f2900edc32" target="_blank"&gt;FetchRSS&lt;/a&gt;生成的提要）&lt;/span&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 19 Mar 2026 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.rand.org/pubs/research_reports/RRA4632-1.html</guid></item><item><title>伊朗升级战略不会奏效</title><link>https://www.rand.org/pubs/commentary/2026/03/irans-escalation-strategy-wont-work.html</link><description>&lt;img height="90" src="https://www.rand.org/content/rand/pubs/commentary/2026/03/irans-escalation-strategy-wont-work/_jcr_content/par/teaser.crop.160x90.cm.jpeg/1773863787866.jpeg" width="160" /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;p class="desc"&gt;德黑兰的“升级到降级”战略可能会适得其反。通过轰炸该地区的朋友和敌人，伊朗最终可能会变得比以往任何时候都更贫穷、更弱、更孤立。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt; &lt;span style="font-size: 12px; color: gray;"&gt;（使用&lt;a href="https://fetchrss.com/feedLink?w=67d7ba1d141b09f2900edc32" target="_blank"&gt;FetchRSS&lt;/a&gt;生成的提要）&lt;/span&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 19 Mar 2026 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.rand.org/pubs/commentary/2026/03/irans-escalation-strategy-wont-work.html</guid></item></channel></rss>